| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3809 — Recovery Inhibition (cactus)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b1deb29a-3122-5dec-a35d-3c18f6c3bfd2"
